OL,6,F"We are not only talking about their
OL,7,Ffuture but their present. What should
OL,8,Fhave been done 20 years ago is what we
OL,9,Fare doing now."
OL,11,FThere are thought to be fewer than 200
OL,12,FGolden Goats in Guernsey.
OL,14,FFrom that number, Peter says only
OL,15,Faround 40 females can be bred, and
OL,16,Fsome owners are reluctant to do so as
OL,17,Fthere is no on-island livestock vet.
