OL,6,FHe explains: "It's only when we have
OL,7,Fcome to analyse those figures on the
OL,8,Fisland that we have realised what a
OL,9,Fdesperate state our iconic breed is in.
OL,11,F"Of all the goats on the island, they
OL,12,Fhave either come directly from this
OL,13,Ffarm or indirectly from our billy
OL,14,Fgoats, which is a staggering thing
OL,15,Fbecause it means your gene pool is
OL,16,Fnarrow."
