OL,6,FThe Golden Guernsey Goat received a
OL,7,Froyal title in July 2024 when the King
OL,8,Fand Queen visited the island, making
OL,9,Fit the only animal breed to have
OL,10,Fformally received such an honour from
OL,11,Fthe Monarch in recent history.
OL,13,FTheir Majesties officially bestowed
OL,14,Fthe title by placing an engraved brass
OL,15,Fbell on a collar around the neck of an
OL,16,Feight-year-old female Golden Guernsey
OL,17,FGoat, Summerville Tamsin.
OL,19,FPeter adds that the goats are part of
OL,20,Fthe island's identity and can be a
OL,21,Fvaluable marketing tool.
