OL,4,Cextinction on home island
OL,6,FHe says: "We have an iconic goat with
OL,7,Fa royal title, which can be used to
OL,8,Fpromote business. I have had people
OL,9,Ffrom cruise ships asking to see the
OL,10,Fgoats in their native island and we
OL,11,Fhave people coming on day trips to see
OL,12,Fthem.
OL,14,F"One of these goats has been here for
OL,15,Fyears; it shows stability, continuity,
OL,16,Fwhich is what finance and commerce are
OL,17,Flooking for in a place to invest and
OL,18,Fto do business in."
