OL,6,FDr Sarah Owens, an American breeder of
OL,7,Fthe Golden Guernsey Goat, is on the
OL,8,Fisland for the international meeting.
OL,10,FShe says: "The beautiful, gentle,
OL,11,Fgenerous Guernsey Goat is on its way
OL,12,Fto becoming as iconic in the US as it
OL,13,Fis in the UK, but it needs a helping
OL,14,Fhand to remain healthy.
OL,16,F"Last year, for the first time in
OL,17,Fnearly two decades, we exchanged
OL,18,Fgenetics across the ocean, and I am so
OL,19,Fexcited that this symposium will link
OL,20,Fus directly to their Guernsey homeland.
