OL,3,CRoyal goat at risk as breed faces
OL,4,Cextinction on home island
OL,6,F"We hope to create a network of expert
OL,7,Fsupport to ensure they continue to
OL,8,Fflourish, both in Guernsey and beyond."
OL,10,FGuernsey Lieutenant-Governor, Lt Gen
OL,11,FSir Richard Cripwell, says it would be
OL,12,Fa "terrible loss" if the breed were to
OL,13,Fdie out on the island.
OL,15,FHe adds: "I don't think people here
OL,16,Frealise that they are hugely popular
OL,17,Fin the United Kingdom and America,
OL,18,Fthis is a much-loved and very useful
OL,19,Fbreed.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
