OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1761077532
OL,3,CRoyal goat at risk as breed faces
OL,4,Cextinction on home island
OL,6,F"It's about making sure that the
OL,7,Ffuture of the goats in these islands
OL,8,Fis as secure as we can make it.
OL,10,F"It would be a terrible loss for the
OL,11,Fisland. It is an animal that doesn't
OL,12,Fsimply look good, it can do a huge
OL,13,Famount of good. It can be a key part
OL,14,Fof conservation, a huge part of
OL,15,Fpreserving and promoting our
OL,16,Fenvironment.
OL,18,F"There is so much to give, and we
OL,19,Fwould regret it hugely if this
OL,20,Fwonderful animal slipped through our
OL,21,Ffingers."
